[I] Intel Processor Microcode Package for Linux

[T] This package is provided for Linux distributors for inclusion in their OS
[T] releases. Intel recommends obtaining the latest MCUs using the OS vendor
[T] update mechanism.

[U] https://github.com/intel/Intel-Linux-Processor-Microcode-Data-Files

[A] Intel
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] base/firmware
[F] CROSS
[K] + linux
[R] + x86 x86-64

[L] Free-to-use
[V] 20260512

[D] cff8ab879a1cd97db6b865c3ea0beeb99024a094bfe6819888b256c3 microcode-20260512.tar.gz https://github.com/intel/Intel-Linux-Processor-Microcode-Data-Files/archive/refs/tags/

